Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能交到新朋友也并不是徒劳无用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让她察觉到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 今天内不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁残念…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在说我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不当弟子的话能不能察觉到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不当弟子 成为朋友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二学期就算交到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让师傅明白自己很强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管强弱 波知应该会很高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过师父可能只把我当成弟子看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟子这个那么看重的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好说 对苏特卡来说是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想想 和全班做朋友也太乱来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过可能觉得不这样的话没法改变的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波知以前那么没用的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一想 和一开始比起来是变强了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 苏特卡什么也没和师父说就迎来了寒假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎来了圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到了新年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了三天 人少了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多摊子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时都是在哪的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们买点不一样的分着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这种系统的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了是可以分的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就选金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金鱼可不是寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什么都没有棉花却不断变大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍术?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 这样就能分…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参拜的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要二礼二拍手一礼 这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二礼二拍手一礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这种念咒一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二礼二拍手一礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然是新年参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说明明是风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳子还念那样的咒语…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仓井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成为坚强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成为完美的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和全班成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和香依和好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和师父…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和师父学习 掌握忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望会有好事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜子没什么想法吗 梦想之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜子的梦想呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有的 但是保密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 波知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超在意超在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的梦想是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为完美的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美的自己?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什么呀 听上去那么傻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仓井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来还要见亲戚的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天想要成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和仓井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是尾仲同学和栗枝同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是过年 大家都来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理实习的时候我还没有好好道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把粉弄得到处都是的那次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得必须变得更坚强点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来苏特卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做朋友那事后来怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 还没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一里也来新年参拜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 烤薄饼那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一起去吃烤薄饼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去 现在就能去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说今天啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要确定什么时候 会联系你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能作为朋友一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说我们早就是烤薄饼朋友了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是香依发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问波知有哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香依?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你能联系上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡拉0K的时候偷偷交换了下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「波知很厉害哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还没治好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香依 等着我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香依?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍个波知的睡颜发给香依
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棉花糖回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚交到朋友了 还是两个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香依
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是和服是甚平呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快点去参拜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望波知能少哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新学期上来就折纸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修行没有休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 一里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 佩可 衣抄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃了薄煎饼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪很奇怪很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁阿鲁阿鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 阿鲁阿鲁阿鲁…  - 怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么叫我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你闲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父叫尾中同学、栗枝同学的时候有「酱」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是朋友了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我却是「苏特卡同学」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为师父和弟子的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:13:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我比她们早认识师父很久的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能已经习惯了呢 叫你「同学」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去说了想成为朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟子这头衔那么重要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为遇见师父的时候对我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏特卡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说能做到全都传给你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有全都传授给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得我不能去说想做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺复杂的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是全部是些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没办法了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才只是想被称呼苏特卡酱 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不是那么复杂的问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能也会因为佩可那边那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称呼你自然也变成苏特卡酱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和波知说过话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信波知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真残念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说残念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我带「同学」很奇怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父一定也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏特卡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I go home
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英文?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good bye everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了明白了 我想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能聊聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 阿鲁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 米艾鲁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米艾鲁?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会讲到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米艾鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了远方 已经见不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在笑什么啊 菜子助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波知都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来干什么的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:16:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说呀 是关于苏特卡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏特卡同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏特卡她呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让你叫她「苏特卡酱」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为苏特卡同学是弟子 没有成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经跟朋友一样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波知就会纠结这种地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏特卡说想这样的 那就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被菜子和阿鲁称呼名字的时候非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想今后能让苏特卡同学也叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就方便说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫苏特卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 波知还有苏特卡真是麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得最麻烦的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能被人打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记日文了 不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要在意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,new 手里剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的手里剑 一起做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起做吧 苏特卡酱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bocchi-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是英文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真历害 真…厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.67,注,NTP,0,0,0,,注:此处二人敬语和比较亲近的说法切换不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这样的手里剑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多种的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 收集各种手里剑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集 去收集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集 收集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴笨也要有限度的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么又在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏特卡还是很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都叫你苏特卡酱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我就不能称呼师父叫「师父」了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系 直接叫波知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波知说全部传授了之后想做朋友的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都传达到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以苏特卡才想和波知做朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜子 阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不当弟子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么好处都给你抢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是丢下我一起回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是超强苏特卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏特卡酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不当弟子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直都很软弱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 反了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为师父很强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父在菜子不及格的时候也让她露出了笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在阿鲁想回家换衣服的时候也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有师父在才能直接来上学的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了这样的师父
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得比起忍者 更想成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父全都传授给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 秘诀皆传
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来做朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏特卡酱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请展开手里剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比起忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更喜欢师父
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次被说要和我做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 师父和我成为了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏特卡酱 同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波知 师父同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我波知就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父才是 已经是朋友就不要叫「同学」了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还疏远了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去外面扔扔看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉变了 又好像没变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个人怎么看都那么要好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:27.23,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あたらしい靴の音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:31.13,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,はじめまして　ペコリおじぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:35.43,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あたらしい自分になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:40.03,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,季節とおなじ　わたしも変わりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:43.23,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ノート埋めたマンガみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:48.44,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,一歩一歩　進んでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:53.34,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,まるで夢で見たようなセリフなので
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:58.03,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,一度は疑ってしまいますけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:01.14,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,パッと笑顔が咲きました
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:04.44,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,七分咲きかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:09.33,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ見慣れないのです　伸びてく影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:13.34,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,通い始めたら舞ってきたかけらたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:20.23,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,正気失ってしまうほどの大事な言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:28.14,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,今日はわたしから「ね、いっしょにかえろ。」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:31.28,ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いっしょに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:27.23,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,崭新的鞋子的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:31.13,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 （点头行礼）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:35.43,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,成为崭新的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:40.03,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,和季节一样   我也想做出改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:43.23,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,就像埋在笔记本里的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:48.44,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,一步一步的前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:53.34,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像只有在梦中才能看到的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:58.03,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一度的怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:01.14,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,突然绽放了笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:04.44,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这只是七分吧
